org.eclipse.viatra.cep.core.metamodels.events

Interface ComplexEventPattern

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, EventPattern, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnonymousComplexEventPattern, ComplexEventPatternImpl, ParameterizableComplexEventPattern

    public interface ComplexEventPattern
extends EventPattern
    A representation of the model object 'Complex Event Pattern'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Operator
    • Timewindow
    • Contained Event Patterns
    • Event Context
    See Also:
    EventsPackage.getComplexEventPattern()
